                            Forschungsumgebung / Beta maṣāḥǝft British Museum,  Akademie der Wissenschaften in Hamburg</dc:publisher><dcterms:isPartOf rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu"/><dcterms:bibliographicCitation>LIT7256PPAndarabbi</dcterms:bibliographicCitation><dc:format>xml</dc:format><dc:language rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#language">en</dc:language><dc:language rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#language">gez</dc:language><dc:contributor>Alessandro Bausi</dc:contributor><dc:contributor>Carsten Hoffmann</dc:contributor><rdf:type rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/Magic"/><rdf:type rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/Prayers"/><rdf:type rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/demon"/><dc:title>Ba-sǝma Sayṭān wǝluda (!) Qǝrṭǝṭāʾel Maržiži</dc:title><dc:title xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ ሰይጣን፡ ውሉደ፡ ቅርጥጣኤል፡ መርዢዢ፡ ...</dc:title><crm:P102_has_title rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7256PPAndarabbi/title/t1" xml:lang="gez"/><dc:title xml:lang="gez">Ba-sǝma Sayṭān wǝluda (!) Qǝrṭǝṭāʾel Maržiži</dc:title><dc:title xml:lang="en">In the name of Satan, son of (!) Qǝrṭǝṭāʾel, Maržiži, ...</dc:title><dc:title xml:lang="gez">ለዝሰይጣን፡ ወለዝ፡ አንደረቢ፡ ለዝ፡ ጋኔን፡ ወለዝ፡ ብእሲ፡ ዘርዝር፡</dc:title><crm:P102_has_title rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7256PPAndarabbi/title/t2" xml:lang="gez"/><dc:title xml:lang="gez">La-zǝ-Sayṭān wa-la-zǝ ʾAndarabbi la-zǝ gānen wa-la-zǝ bǝʾsi Zarzǝr</dc:title><dc:title xml:lang="en">To Satan and to ʾAndarabbi, to this demon and to this Zarzǝr-man</dc:title><dc:title xml:lang="en">Prayer and prescription against demons and against magicians who cast spells by throwing stones</dc:title><dcterms:hasPart rdf:resource="LIT7256PPAndarabbi/part/div1"/><dcterms:hasPart rdf:resource="LIT7256PPAndarabbi/part/div2"/></rdf:Description><oa:Annotation rdf:about="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7256PPAndarabbi/person/annotation/1"><oa:hasTarget rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7256PPAndarabbi"/><oa:hasBody rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11330Devil"/><oa:annotatedAt rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date">2026-04-05+02:00</oa:annotatedAt><lawd:hasName>Satan</lawd:hasName></oa:Annotation><rdf:Description rdf:about="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7256PPAndarabbi/part/div1"><dcterms:isPartOf rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7256PPAndarabbi"/><rdf:type rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/part"/></rdf:Description><rdf:Description rdf:about="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7256PPAndarabbi/part/div2"><dcterms:isPartOf rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7256PPAndarabbi"/><rdf:type rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/part"/></rdf:Description><rdf:Description rdf:about="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7256PPAndarabbi/title/t1"><rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/E35_Title"/><rdfs:label>በስመ፡ ሰይጣን፡ ውሉደ፡ ቅርጥጣኤል፡ መርዢዢ፡ ...</rdfs:label></rdf:Description><rdf:Description rdf:about="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7256PPAndarabbi/title/t2"><rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/E35_Title"/><rdfs:label>ለዝሰይጣን፡ ወለዝ፡ አንደረቢ፡ ለዝ፡ ጋኔን፡ ወለዝ፡ ብእሲ፡ ዘርዝር፡</rdfs:label></rdf:Description></rdf:RDF>